&lt;p&gt;We&#39;re the team behind &lt;a href=&quot;https://up.com.au&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Up&lt;/a&gt;, but under the hood, we&#39;re Ferocia - a passionate tech company driven by financial inclusion. Since 2011, we&#39;ve been crafting innovative financial tools, starting with the digital platform for Bendigo Bank. We believe technology can empower everyone, from the advantaged to the disadvantaged, which is why Up was born.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Now, as part of the &lt;a href=&quot;https://bendigoadelaide.com.au/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Bendigo and Adelaide Bank&lt;/a&gt; family, we combine the agility of a small company with the reach and stability of a major player. Together, we&#39;re &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.bendigoadelaide.com.au/esg/environment/climate-change/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;carbon neutral&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.bendigoadelaide.com.au/community/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;community-focused&lt;/a&gt;, and dedicated to high standards of &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.bendigoadelaide.com.au/esg/governance/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;corporate governance&lt;/a&gt;. Our mission? To leverage technology to help Australians move from financial stress and anxiety to a place of confidence and empowerment.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Want to join us? We&#39;d love to hear from you!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3&gt;The Gig&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We’re on the lookout for passionate, experienced problem-solvers to join our Melbourne-based crew as we continue guiding over 1,000,000 Upsiders towards feeling&amp;nbsp;&lt;em&gt;really&lt;/em&gt; good about money.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our Phone Support currently runs Monday - Friday from 9am - 5pm with a possibility of expanding hours as we grow, working hand-in-hand with our turbocharged in-app chat, Talk to Us - both powered by our four signature Support values. Your mission? To bring those values to life in every conversation on the Phone and be the magic behind Up Support.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You’ll be the ultimate go-to guru, tackling all sorts of questions, teaming up with your fellow support heroes, and making sure every Upsider gets the help they need. You’ll work side-by-side with our Account Verification and Talk to Us squads while mastering our in-house support software (aka your new best friend).&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As the expert in this space, you won’t just &lt;em&gt;do&lt;/em&gt; phone support - you’ll help shape it. Your voice matters, and you’ll have the power to reimagine the support experience, provide feedback, and collaborate with the wider team to take things to the next level.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you’ve got customer service experience specifically with phone support and/or banking experience (preferred but not a dealbreaker) and are ready to be part of something awesome - let’s talk!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Experience, knowledge &amp;amp; skills&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li data-path-to-node=&quot;2,0,0&quot;&gt;Melbourne-based and keen to work from our Collins Street (Melbourne CBD) office as often as possible.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-path-to-node=&quot;2,1,0&quot;&gt;Banking experience and knowledge of banking systems (preferred, but not a deal-breaker).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-path-to-node=&quot;2,2,0&quot;&gt;Previous customer service experience, with a background in phone-based support.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-path-to-node=&quot;2,3,0&quot;&gt;A track record of driving process improvements and finding better ways to do things.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-path-to-node=&quot;2,4,0&quot;&gt;Tech-savvy with the ability to adapt to new systems and tools quickly.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-path-to-node=&quot;2,5,0&quot;&gt;Be Up for change and adaptable in an evolving environment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
